text: Friedrich Hermann von Schönberg, 1st Duke of Schomberg, 1st Count of Mertola, (; ; 6 December 1615 – 1 July 1690) was a Marshal of France and a General in the English and Portuguese Army. He was killed at the Battle of the Boyne in 1690. == References == Category:Marshals of France Category:1615 births Category:1690 deaths Category:Generals Category:People from Heidelberg Category:Dukes and duchesses
